Insider Activity


Individual




Howard H. Xia



Dr. Howard H. Xia is on the Board of Directors at II-VI, Inc. Dr. Xia was previously employed as General Manager by Vodafone China Ltd., Director-Technology Strategy by AirTouch Communications, and Director-Technology Strategy by Vodafone AirTouch Plc. He received his undergraduate degree from South China Normal University, a graduate degree from New York University Polytechnic School of Engineering and a doctorate degree from New York University Polytechnic School of Engineering.



